videos.headline: Chris Boucher breaks ankles and gets the and-1 layup

videos.description: Alabama thinks it's getting two points until Dylan Ennis comes out of nowhere with a vicious block, starting a fast break for Oregon and an easy layup at the other end.
videos.headline: Epic block leads to easy layup for Oregon
Braxton Key gets the rebound and makes the layup

videos.description: Donta Hall flies over the defenders for a two-handed slam that gets the approval of Brad Daugherty.
videos.headline: Hall's massive slam has Brad Daugherty pumped up

videos.description: No. 24 Oregon ends the game on a 9-0 run to defeat Alabama 65-56.
videos.headline: Oregon surges late to top Alabama
